---
title: "Best method name" contest 2008
date: 2015-06-13 22:01 UTC
tags: ruby,method
---


~~~ruby
    def shutdown_system!
      system "sudo shutdown -h 1"
    end

    def shuldown_system? # Winner of 'best method name contest 2008 '
      system "sudo shutdown -h 1" if options[:autoshutdownd] || options[:asd]
    end
~~~

